{
  "stem": "27150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, I just took it as it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, that means by-- I finished school before Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they made a lot of jokes about Hitler and things, and then that he was a painter, and what it means, heil, Hitler.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, well, he was a painter, so up to here, oil paint, other, you'd see here's rubber, it's plastic.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were revues, see, at the Sunday [INAUDIBLE] were making jokes about Hitler, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "-- that before he went into-- came to power, and even after, you see-- you see very-- a few caricatures in the papers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At first, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on, you see, there was-- I don't know whether you heard about it-- Poland became independent in 1918.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After the Bolshevik War, there was the first election, and then the right wing took over government.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put everything, all the heroes who fought for independence, aside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in 1926, Marshal Pilsudski, you see, took over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, he-- part of the army was for him-- you see, mostly central and south, while the west were rightists, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a few days' revolution.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember, you see, there was shooting and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then Pilsudski went-- took, took over, and he kept the job of Defense Minister, but he was running the show.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a Premier and a Foreign Minister, but Pilsudski was running the show.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And during his time, it was very good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was very liberal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was himself delivering speeches, criticizing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You see, he just could say that the Parliament is a brothel, and something like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You see, he died in 1935 or 1936, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
